Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:20.54,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5\fs25\pos(801,54)}Egoist
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:20.54,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}利他主义者终将成为利己主义者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:23.46,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}真是罪恶的法则啊
